snippet.title: YO-KAI WATCH BLASTERS: Red Cat Corps & White Dog Squad - Launch Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Assemble your own Blasters crew and fight your way through action-packed battles in YO-KAI WATCH BLASTERS: Red Cat Corps and YO-KAI WATCH BLASTERS: White Dog Squad, out now on Nintendo 3DS family systems!

Official Website: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Misc-/YO-KAI-WATCH-BLASTERS-1425562.html?utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=YOKAIWATCHBLASTERS%7Cw36
